description: Seeks to provide a moderate and sustainable level of current income. Invests primarily in U.S. agency mortgage-backed pass-through securities issued by Ginnie Mae (GNMA), Fannie Mae (FNMA), and Freddie Mac (FHLMC). Moderate interest rate risk, with a dollar-weighted average maturity of 3 to 10 years.
name: Vanguard Mortgage-Backed Securities ETF
